Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人要來了 小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思維會被牠侵蝕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果回答了 人類就會滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體 不聽使喚…！
