Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 慶樹島的空中設施60%損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛瑠島包括一部分跑道在內的第二次裝備全毀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,損失慘重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三棟房屋被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失蹤人數目前為28 但已確認到其中二人的生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向島迎擊系統全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…我們的島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親…戰死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令代為指揮的戰鬥 你認為如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為 那是當時的最佳選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你指揮的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假設的情境我無意奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今後準備怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要在這兒站多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先失陪了 我還有分析敵人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況應該早就在意料之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 今晚一定要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來 還有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去問你爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他…也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 傷患還多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去叫真壁叔叔來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 再給我一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想他應該沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天能來上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我一定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 進屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 今晚一定要好好休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽 你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西你從哪撿回來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的什麼話 這是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家…在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得讓他努力才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我們家叫「春日井」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是孩子就是紐帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.90,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：春日井和紐帶同音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爸你好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的人是紐帶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連燈都不開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸 你爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（part-b）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛那東西的感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼特別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定吃驚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們居然在幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 如果我說日本已經不存在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 日本…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是29年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京呢 大阪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島就已經從地圖上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是覺得難以置信？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這種東西就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到昨天為止 唯有這個島才是樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能得救 是多虧了校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是多虧了你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們還會再來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會和我一起戰鬥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你特地過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於一騎的身體 有些話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有教工會議所以回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你還想騙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成…你生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生給了我這套衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你今天不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想想要是沒有我 你連飯都不會做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸我以前也是自己做飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是結婚之前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 今晚我來露一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西 我已經在今天失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 待在這裡我更平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才聊的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是假設是我指揮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換成是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是皆城…前司令把你分配到CDC的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 不賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這米你都沒洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的事 你都知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別問我為什麼要瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和總士一起戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生都跟你說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 法芙娜的訓練就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於一騎的身體 有些話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記錄顯示 他在駕駛中的意識和平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…戰鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的染色體出現了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不能斷定 需要觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過繼續這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:19:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅音 對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏前原來是機器人的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她才沒和我們一起去避難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏前她去戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 爸爸不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個機器人我也能開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒開玩笑吧 搞不好會沒命的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 一騎去開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城和一騎最近好像經常去地下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我也想一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哪個一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎他好像很努力的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 把衣服全脫了然後走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 全脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放進後面的洗衣櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你回來的時候就洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是殺菌燈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩眼直視前方走過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 從我這裡看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 又要痛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上這套協同作用服就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協同作…用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是會痛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事…你告訴他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把之前的戰鬥數據連同整個駕駛座都轉移過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下次戰鬥應該就能輕鬆點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 現在開始進行Mk.Ⅺ的戰鬥系統測試
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齊格飛系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在了解一切之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會得知世界的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會知道力量的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會明白夢醒之日總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還以為這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都能夠克服
